00:00:21,992 --> 00:00:25,297
So the Buddha meets this Jain who's called Upali.

5
00:00:25,878 --> 00:00:33,969
And it links in with Last Moon, although it's not necessary to have listened to the Last Moon one, about chaitanya, about will.

6
