8
00:00:49,340 --> 00:00:57,758
All experience, all actions are preceded by the mind, led by the mind, made by the mind.

9
00:00:58,499 --> 00:01:06,977
Speak or act with a corrupted mind and suffering follows as the wagon wheel follows the hoof of an ox.

10
00:01:09,454 --> 00:01:34,703
and the opposite all experience is preceded by mind led by mind made by mind speak or act with a peaceful mind or a wholesome mind and happiness follows like a never departing shadow okay so here we have this discourse for those of you want to know it's the in the majima nikai number 56 the middle length sayings number 56.

11
00:01:35,441 --> 00:01:53,585
so the buddha is at nalanda which was a big town and became a very important university university town a big study town and at the same time the jain leader had turned up with his group of monks and nuns

