And the Buddha replies that the Tathagata doesn't use the word rod, he uses the word action.

43
00:05:39,095 --> 00:05:40,317
So he says, well, okay.

44
00:05:41,192 --> 00:05:48,709
Which of these actions does the friend Gautama describe as making evil karma the production of karma?

45
00:05:48,728 --> 00:05:53,839
Well, there are three actions, the body, the speech and the mind.

46
00:05:54,982 --> 00:06:00,112
And is bodily action one thing, verbal action another, mental action

47
00:06:00,245 --> 00:06:00,966
Still another.

48
00:06:01,607 --> 00:06:03,029
