53
00:06:35,185 --> 00:06:36,507
I said mental action.

54
00:06:36,786 --> 00:06:39,970
Did you say mental action, friend Gautama?

55
00:06:40,391 --> 00:06:42,713
I said mental action, Digha Tapasi.

56
00:06:43,153 --> 00:06:46,237
Are you sure you said mental action, friend Gautama?

57
00:06:46,536 --> 00:06:49,000
I did say mental action.

58
00:06:50,583 --> 00:06:53,267
So at this point, the Jain leaves.

59
00:06:53,307 --> 00:06:53,910
He's had enough.

60
00:06:54,250 --> 00:06:55,533
